Support
For questions, bug reports, and any other concerns, please email:
hotavocadoapps@gmail.com
We'll get right back to you as soon as we can.
Privacy Policy
Hot Avocado Apps is committed to protecting the privacy of our users. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect the information of users of our mobile apps, MyGames Database and Task Attack.
Information Collection
Neither MyGames Database nor Task Attack collect any personally identifiable information from users. The only information collected is standard crash log data to help improve the apps' performance.
MyGames Database also uses a third-party analytics service to anonymously collect information about user-initiated events within the app. This data is used to understand how the app is being used and to make improvements.
Information Use and Sharing
Any information collected is used solely for the purpose of improving the apps and their performance. Hot Avocado Apps does not sell, trade, or share user information with any third parties, except for the anonymous analytics data collected by MyGames Database.
Data Security
Hot Avocado Apps takes reasonable measures to protect the information collected from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.
User Rights
Users have the right to request deletion of any data collected about them. To do so, please contact us at
hotavocadoapps@gmail.com
.
Updates to this Policy
Hot Avocado Apps may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Users will be notified of any changes.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
hotavocadoapps@gmail.com
.
